## AGH {{ .Version }}

AGH is an Agent Operating System for running ACP-compatible coding agents as managed sessions.

### Installation

#### Binary Download
Download the appropriate `agh_{{ .Version }}_<os>_<arch>.tar.gz` asset for your platform and extract it.

#### Go Install
```bash
go install github.com/pedronauck/agh/cmd/agh@{{ .Tag }}
```
